On Sunday radio personalities Maina Kageni and Adelle Onyango were in Monaco for the Formula One Grand Prix, as part of the ongoing Johnnie Walker Promotion. Adelle, the Kiss FM presenter known for her breakfast with the stars show, said it was the best experience of her life. We can confirm that she rode on yachts worth millions of dollars. She and Classic 105 presenter Maina were joined by other Diageo Global Influencers in Monaco. The Monaco Grand Prix has been described as the Jewel in the Formula One crown. Speaking to Word Is Adelle said, "The whole experience was mind blowing! I got to learn about whisky and F1 in a way that I had never had before." "Everyone needs to experience this." She is now officially a Formula One fan.